ocaml-cppffigen Version 0.003
-----------------------------

* [13 Feb 2025] a bunch of changs
  * added a bunch more static typing to the generatd C++ code, in order to sure better automatic conversions

  * switched from ppx_sexp_conv to pa_ppx.deriving_plugins.sexp

  * switched to using pa_ppx_fmtformat for generating code

  * removed dependency on pcre (why was it ever needed?)

